      <title>中国开发商万科寻求改变两笔银行贷款的条款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/chinese-developer-vanke-seeks-to-alter-terms-on-two-bank-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，受长期房地产危机影响，万科企业财务状况进一步恶化，该公司正寻求贷款方批准更改两笔境外贷款的条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/chinese-developer-vanke-seeks-to-alter-terms-on-two-bank-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate>
